AD_MODULE.NAME: Standard Roles
AD_MODULE.DESCRIPTION: Pre-configured collection of standard ERP roles
AD_MODULE.HELP: This dataset contains the following roles with their access to corresponding Openbravo entities - windows, reports, actions. * Employee - Any person of the enterprise * Purchase manager - User working in the procurement department * Sales - User working in the sales department * Material management - User working in the warehouse * Finance - Users working in the Finance department * Company Executive - Senior management * Company admin - The administrator of the company
